Class MovableObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • spacesurvival.model.gameobject.GameObject
      • spacesurvival.model.gameobject.movable.MovableObject
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Collideable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Bullet, MainObject
    public abstract class MovableObject
extends GameObject
    An object which can move, extends a basic game object and implements a logic for movement and an optional target.
